             sworn.</p>
               <p>I am a watchman; I took charge of the prisoner.</p>
               <p>PRISONER's DEFENCE.</p>
               <p>The gentleman was very much in liquor and began pulling me about; I called for assistance; he struck me in the ribs several times, and said, where is my watch?</p>
